2016年6月開始的'''阿勒頗攻勢'''是敘利亞政府軍在[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]發起的軍事行動，試圖切斷反對派僅餘的通往阿勒頗的最後補給路線。<ref name="unleashes">{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-06/26/c_135467722.htm|title=Syrian army unleashes broad offensive in Aleppo|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202113025/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-06/26/c_135467722.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.morningstaronline.co.uk/a-4241-Syria-Army-bid-to-cut-off-Aleppo-unleashes-fierce-fighting#.V3WUhut96Uk|title=Syria: Army bid to cut off Aleppo unleashes fierce fighting|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630013917/http://www.morningstaronline.co.uk/a-4241-Syria-Army-bid-to-cut-off-Aleppo-unleashes-fierce-fighting#.V3WUhut96Uk|archivedate=2016年6月30日|df=}}</ref>

到7月下旬，政府軍對阿勒頗反對派控制區完成包圍，反對派其後多次發起反攻企圖解除包圍，到8月6日終於在阿勒頗西南部成功打通一條新通道。政府軍於9月4日再次成功合圍。

==初期攻勢==
在俄軍大舉空襲後，本次攻勢於2016年6月25日開始。<ref name="heavy">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/heavy-russian-airstrikes-aleppo/|title=Heavy Russian airstrikes on Aleppo amid preparations for huge ground offensive|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=25 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816083308/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/heavy-russian-airstrikes-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>地面部隊開始前進之前，先以猛烈炮火轟擊敵方。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1718716/syrian-government-forces-close-in-on-aleppo|title=Syrian Government Forces Close In On Aleppo|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701095313/http://news.sky.com/story/1718716/syrian-government-forces-close-in-on-aleppo|dead-url=no}}</ref>敘軍試圖在阿勒頗西北部推進，並試圖逼近反對派僅餘的補給線卡斯泰洛路（Castello Road）。到次日早晨時，俄軍在5小時內進行了超過60次空襲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russians-launch-60-airstrikes-northern-aleppo/|title=Russians launches non-stop air campaign over northern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=26 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109000137/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russians-launch-60-airstrikes-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

6月26日，敘軍攻入馬拉農場（Mallah Farms）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-syrian-army-advances-northern-aleppo-amid-intensifying-battles/|title=Field Report: Syrian Army advances in northern Aleppo amid intensifying battles|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=26 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2018-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016044341/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-syrian-army-advances-northern-aleppo-amid-intensifying-battles/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月28日，敘軍已攻佔馬拉農場一半地方。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/story/syrian-government-forces-close-in-on-aleppo-10327447 |title=Syrian Government Forces Close In On Aleppo |publisher= |date=2016-06-30 |access-date=2016-08-05 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427124200/https://news.sky.com/story/syrian-government-forces-close-in-on-aleppo-10327447 |dead-url=no }}</ref>卡斯泰洛路已落入敘軍地面炮火射程範圍內。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syrian-troops-capture-important-area-near-the-city-of-aleppo/2016/06/28/1109d1fa-3d26-11e6-9e16-4cf01a41decb_story.html|title=US-backed Syrian rebels move toward IS-held town near Iraq|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822035609/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syrian-troops-capture-important-area-near-the-city-of-aleppo/2016/06/28/1109d1fa-3d26-11e6-9e16-4cf01a41decb_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>俄軍持續猛烈空襲反對派武裝，單在6月27日早上已在Handarat山區和Anadan平原進行了30次空襲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-air-force-strikes-northern-aleppo-amid-syrian-army-advance/|title=Russian Air Force strikes northern Aleppo amid Syrian Army advance|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=27 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106013945/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-air-force-strikes-northern-aleppo-amid-syrian-army-advance/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

6月29日，反對派在馬拉的一次反攻被擊退。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-jihadi-rebels-attack-northern-aleppo-repelled/|title=Field Report: Jihadi rebels attack on northern Aleppo repelled|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=29 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093702/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-jihadi-rebels-attack-northern-aleppo-repelled/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同日稍後，反對派以兩次自殺式汽車炸彈攻擊逼使敘軍放棄先前在馬拉取得的進展。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2016/Jun-30/359897-at-least-70-killed-in-north-of-syrias-aleppo-activists.ashx|title=At least 70 killed in north of Syria's Aleppo: activists|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093705/https://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2016/Jun-30/359897-at-least-70-killed-in-north-of-syrias-aleppo-activists.ashx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="withdraws">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-withdraws-al-malaah-farms-northern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army withdraws from Al-Malaah Farms in northern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=29 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109000155/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-withdraws-al-malaah-farms-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>6月30日，敘軍奪回前一天的所有失地。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recaptures-lost-points-al-malaah-farms-northern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army recaptures all lost points at Al-Malaah Farms in northern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=30 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093719/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recaptures-lost-points-al-malaah-farms-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

7月2日至3日，敘軍攻入馬拉南部，進一步逼近卡斯泰洛路。<ref name="keyfarms">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2016/Jul-03/360301-syria-government-rebels-battle-for-key-farms-north-of-aleppo-activists.ashx|title=Syria government, rebels battle for key farms north of Aleppo: activists|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009180848/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2016/Jul-03/360301-syria-government-rebels-battle-for-key-farms-north-of-aleppo-activists.ashx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-key-jihadist-area-northern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Armed Forces advance at key jihadist area in northern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702084819/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-key-jihadist-area-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月3日，俄軍一枚巡航導彈據報摧毀了反對派在阿勒頗西部的一個[[BGM-71拖式飛彈|BGM-71拖式飛彈]]儲存庫。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-cruise-missile-obliterates-rebel-tow-storage-base-western-aleppo/|title=Russian cruise missile obliterates rebel TOW storage base in western Aleppo|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=3 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203172509/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-cruise-missile-obliterates-rebel-tow-storage-base-western-aleppo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>7月4日，反對派的一次反攻被擊退。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/videos-syrian-army-advances-urban-warfare-aleppo-city/|title=VIDEOS: Syrian Army advances during urban warfare in Aleppo city|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=3 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093747/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/videos-syrian-army-advances-urban-warfare-aleppo-city/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/aleppo-battle-update-syrian-army-foils-rebels-attack-northern-aleppo/|title=Aleppo Battle Update: Syrian Army foils rebel attack in northern Aleppo|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=4 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115151806/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/aleppo-battle-update-syrian-army-foils-rebels-attack-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>敘軍繼續向馬拉南部推進，並擊退反對派另一次的反攻。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-northern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army advances in northern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=4 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816144808/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-foils-massive-jihadist-counter-offensive-northern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army foils massive jihadist counter-offensive in northern Aleppo|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=5 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816165431/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-foils-massive-jihadist-counter-offensive-northern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月7日，親政府部隊攻佔馬拉南部，距離卡斯泰洛路不到1公里，<ref name="cut">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKCN0ZN0U2|title=Syrian army fire cuts only road into rebel-held Aleppo: rebels|work=Reuters|date=7 July 2016|accessdate=2016-08-04|archive-date=2016-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217061711/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKCN0ZN0U2|dead-url=no}}</ref>並攻佔俯瞰卡斯泰洛路的一座小山。<ref name="truce">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3678994/Fierce-fighting-key-Aleppo-road-despite-Syria-truce.html|title=Fierce fighting for key Aleppo road despite Syria truce|publisher=|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-08-04|archive-date=2016-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918064306/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3678994/Fierce-fighting-key-Aleppo-road-despite-Syria-truce.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36735196|title=Syria conflict: Army fire 'cuts key Aleppo road'|work=BBC News|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-08-04|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915102612/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36735196|dead-url=no}}</ref>敘軍的火炮已足以封鎖卡斯泰洛路，這意味反對派通往阿勒頗的最後一條補給線已被切斷。反對派試圖奪回該座小山但被擊退。<ref name="truce"/>

7月9日，反對派以自殺式汽車炸彈客為先鋒，向卡斯泰洛路附近的敘軍據點展開反攻，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/rocket-attacks-kill-30-syrias-aleppo-40455571|title=Syria's Military Extends Cease-Fire but No Letup in Fighting|first=ABC|last=News|publisher=|accessdate=12 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712033329/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/rocket-attacks-kill-30-syrias-aleppo-40455571|dead-url=no}}</ref>最終被擊退<ref name="sufferheavy">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-rebels-suffer-heavy-casualties-failed-northern-aleppo-offensive/|title=Jihadist rebels suffer heavy casualties in failed northern Aleppo offensive|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=9 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=12 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816174109/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-rebels-suffer-heavy-casualties-failed-northern-aleppo-offensive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當日夜間，反對派集結兵力準備再次反攻，俄軍對通往馬拉農場的道路上的反對派部隊展開猛烈空襲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-jets-swarm-northern-aleppo-jihadists-attempt-retake-castillo-highway/|title=Russian jets swarm northern Aleppo as jihadists attempt to retake Castillo Highway|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=10 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=12 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109011759/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-jets-swarm-northern-aleppo-jihadists-attempt-retake-castillo-highway/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到次日，反對派在馬拉的反攻已停止。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/31237/Opposition_forces_stop_its_military_campaign_in_Malah|title=Opposition forces stop its military campaign in Malah - Qasion News Agency|publisher=|accessdate=12 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114233253/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/31237/Opposition_forces_stop_its_military_campaign_in_Malah|dead-url=no}}</ref>總計有29至75名反對派武裝分子在反攻中陣亡。<ref name="failed">{{cite web|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/syria-rebels-failed-bid-reopen-aleppo-route-1522632171|title=Syria rebels in failed bid to reopen Aleppo route|publisher=|accessdate=12 July 2016|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019185109/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/syria-rebels-failed-bid-reopen-aleppo-route-1522632171|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="75jihadists">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/75-jihadists-7-commanders-killed-mallah-rebel-sources/|title=75 jihadists, 7 commanders killed in Mallah - rebel sources|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=10 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=12 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093902/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/75-jihadists-7-commanders-killed-mallah-rebel-sources/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

7月12日，反對派再次向馬拉發起反攻，到次日被擊退。<ref name="headway">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/video-islamists-rebels-make-headway-northern-aleppo-full-report/|title=VIDEO: Islamists rebels make headway in northern Aleppo - full report|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=13 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=15 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093923/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/video-islamists-rebels-make-headway-northern-aleppo-full-report/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="food">{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/syrias-aleppo-running-out-of-food-medicine-after-regime-forces-advance-1468420678|title=Syria’s Aleppo Running Out of Food, Medicine After Regime Forces Advance|first=Raja|last=Abdulrahim|date=13 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=15 July 2016|via=Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410233735/https://www.wsj.com/articles/syrias-aleppo-running-out-of-food-medicine-after-regime-forces-advance-1468420678|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==敘軍合圍==
7月17日，敘政府軍與真主黨部隊推進至卡斯泰洛路，反對派控制的阿勒頗東部完全陷入包圍。<ref name="reaches">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKCN0ZX09Q|title=Syrian army seizes only road into rebel-held Aleppo|date=2016-07-17|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-21|via=Reuters|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114130140/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKCN0ZX09Q|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2016/07/17/syrian-troops-besiege-rebel-held-parts-aleppo.html |title=Syrian troops besiege rebel-held parts of Aleppo |date=2016-07-17 |work=AP |accessdate= |via=Fox News |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305063319/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2016/07/17/syrian-troops-besiege-rebel-held-parts-aleppo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-advance-north-aleppo/|title=Tiger Forces advance in North Aleppo - Map update|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=17 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816170901/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-advance-north-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>敘軍隨即在卡斯泰洛路堆起沙包路障。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2016/Jul-17/362497-rebel-held-areas-of-syrias-aleppo-fully-besieged-activists.ashx#.V4tFITwUc74.twitter|title=Syrian regime besiege rebel parts of Aleppo|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108233242/https://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2016/Jul-17/362497-rebel-held-areas-of-syrias-aleppo-fully-besieged-activists.ashx#.V4tFITwUc74.twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日稍後，反對派向卡斯泰洛路發起反攻，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-launch-massive-offensive-north-aleppo/|title=Jihadists launch massive offensive in north Aleppo|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=17 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116060046/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-launch-massive-offensive-north-aleppo/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到7月18日，該次反攻被擊退。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.farsnews.com/newstext.aspx?nn=13950428001105|title=Farsnews|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820180204/http://en.farsnews.com/newstext.aspx?nn=13950428001105|archive-date=2016-08-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

一位反對派指揮官表示他們沒有通往外界的地道，包圍圈內有30萬人，而倉存糧食僅夠支撐兩三個月。<ref name="reaches"/>

7月20日，反對派向卡斯泰洛路發起的另一次反攻被擊退。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-foil-jihadist-offensive-begins/|title=Tiger Forces foil jihadist offensive before it begins|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=20 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107093946/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/tiger-forces-foil-jihadist-offensive-begins/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>7月21日，反對派在地道引爆炸彈，38名親政府部隊士兵喪生。<ref name=38government>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36868706 |title=Syria war: Aleppo tunnel bomb 'kills 38 government troops' |work=BBC News |language=en |date=2016-07-22 |accessdate=2016-08-03 |archive-date=2016-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227192218/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36868706 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月26日，敘軍在阿勒頗西北部攻佔更多地方。<ref name="key">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-seizes-key-district-aleppo-city/|title=Syrian Army seizes key district in Aleppo City|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=26 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=26 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817212457/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-seizes-key-district-aleppo-city/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.breitbart.com/news/syria-regime-advances-on-rebels-in-aleppo-monitor/|title=Syria regime advances on rebels in Aleppo: monitor - Breitbart|publisher=|accessdate=28 July 2016|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919041210/http://www.breitbart.com/news/syria-regime-advances-on-rebels-in-aleppo-monitor/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="fire">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-imposes-fire-control-rebel-stronghold-aleppo-city-map/|title=Syrian Army imposes fire control over rebel stronghold in Aleppo City: map|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=26 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=26 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817012811/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-imposes-fire-control-rebel-stronghold-aleppo-city-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月27日，反對派部隊攻擊阿勒頗的庫爾德人控制區，但被庫族部隊擊退。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/kurdish-forces-beat-back-jihadist-rebels-aleppo-city/|title=Kurdish forces beat back jihadist rebels in Aleppo City|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=27 July 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=27 July 2016|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514155555/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/kurdish-forces-beat-back-jihadist-rebels-aleppo-city/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日稍後，敘利亞軍方正式宣佈已切斷反對派所有通往阿勒頗的補給路線。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUKKCN1071FO|title=Syrian army says cut off all supply routes into east Aleppo|publisher=|accessdate=28 July 2016|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514154057/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUKKCN1071FO|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月28日，敘利亞總統[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]宣佈特赦那些在今後3個月內向政府歸降的武裝分子。<ref name=xh01>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/local/2016-07/29/c_129187614.htm |title=俄叙开展联合人道救援 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-07-29 |accessdate=2016-08-04 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305072644/http://news.xinhuanet.com/local/2016-07/29/c_129187614.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>俄羅斯國防部長[[谢尔盖·绍伊古|谢尔盖·绍伊古]]表示總統普京下令在阿勒頗外圍展開大規模的人道主義救援行動，幫助那些被恐怖分子脅持的平民和有意放下武器的武裝分子。紹伊古表示有3條人道主義走廊開放讓居民離開。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russia-launches-large-scale-humanitarian-operation-aleppo/|title=Russia launches large-scale humanitarian operation in Aleppo|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=28 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=1 August 2016|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930123014/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russia-launches-large-scale-humanitarian-operation-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>反對派阻止居民經人道主義走廊離開，只有很少居民成功離開被包圍的反對派控制區。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.breitbart.com/news/un-seeks-control-of-russia-escape-corridors-out-of-aleppo/|title=UN seeks control of Russia escape corridors out of Aleppo - Breitbart|publisher=|accessdate=1 August 2016|archive-date=2019-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190206200247/https://www.breitbart.com/news/un-seeks-control-of-russia-escape-corridors-out-of-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syria-rebels-prevent-civilians-leaving-aleppo-monitor/|title=Syria rebels prevent civilians from leaving Aleppo: monitor|first=News|last=Desk|date=29 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=1 August 2016|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930121501/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syria-rebels-prevent-civilians-leaving-aleppo-monitor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>估計有約10,000名反對派武裝分子在包圍圈內。<ref name=sputnik20160730>{{Cite news |url=http://sputniknews.com/middleeast/20160729/1043768753/aleppo-liberation-military-challenges.html |title=Aleppo's Liberation is Close, But It'll Be a Tough Slog |publisher=Sputnik |date=2016-07-30 |accessdate=2016-08-05 |archive-date=2016-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819011530/http://sputniknews.com/middleeast/20160729/1043768753/aleppo-liberation-military-challenges.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==反對派解圍戰==
7月31日，[[征服軍|征服軍]]在阿勒頗以南和以北發起反攻，試圖解除阿勒頗之圍。據報反對派投入8,000至10,000名戰士、95輛坦克和大量[[自殺炸彈|自殺炸彈]]客進行反攻。<ref name="regainlost">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-3720636/Syrian-army-allies-counter-attack-regain-lost-ground-Aleppo.html|title=Syrian army, allies counter-attack to regain lost ground in Aleppo|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-04|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019073923/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-3720636/Syrian-army-allies-counter-attack-regain-lost-ground-Aleppo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rolls">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-rolls-back-jihadist-gains-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army rolls back jihadist gains in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=3 August 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-04|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514161513/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-rolls-back-jihadist-gains-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>俄軍對反對派展開猛烈空襲，試圖擊退反對派的進攻。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-air-force-emerges-southern-aleppo-help-drive-back-jihadists/|title=Russian Air Force emerges in southern Aleppo to help drive back jihadists|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=31 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=1 August 2016|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514174425/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-air-force-emerges-southern-aleppo-help-drive-back-jihadists/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月1日，俄羅斯軍方宣稱敘政府軍和民兵在俄羅斯空軍支援下，在阿勒頗擊退反對派部隊的進攻，共消滅800多名武裝分子，擊毀14輛坦克和10輛[[步兵战车|步兵戰車]]。<ref name=sputnik20160802>{{Cite news |url=http://sputniknews.cn/military/20160802/1020375370.html |title=俄空天军支援叙政府军在阿勒颇市击退进攻 消灭武装分子800余人 |publisher=俄羅斯衛星網 |date=2016-08-02 |accessdate=2016-08-04 |archive-date=2016-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160802172214/http://sputniknews.cn/military/20160802/1020375370.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月2日，反對派向阿勒頗西南部的拉穆薩（Ramouseh）區發起進攻，<ref name="bid">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-jihadists-aleppo-advance-amid-bid-lift-siege-map-update/|title=Field Report: jihadists in Aleppo advance amid bid to lift siege. Map Update|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=2 August 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 August 2016|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201212753/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-jihadists-aleppo-advance-amid-bid-lift-siege-map-update/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>最終被擊退。

8月4日，反對派向拉穆薩區和-{Al-‘Amariyah}-區發起進攻，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-launch-massive-assault-southern-aleppo/ |title=Jihadists launch massive assault on southern Aleppo |access-date=2016-08-06 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125083330/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-launch-massive-assault-southern-aleppo/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>攻佔-{Al-‘Amariyah}-區和附近的一座小山，或至少一部分。8月5日，敘軍收復在4日的失地，包括-{Al-‘Amariyah}-區在內。<ref>[https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-airstrikes-propel-syrian-army-southern-aleppo/ Russian airstrikes propel the Syrian Army in southern Aleppo] {{Wayback|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-airstrikes-propel-syrian-army-southern-aleppo/ |date=20190514164417 }}, 2016-08-05.</ref>

8月5日稍後[[征服軍|征服軍]]進攻位於拉穆薩區的軍事學院，以[[自殺炸彈|自殺炸彈]]汽車加上猛烈炮轟突破政府軍陣地，<ref name="repelled">[http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKCN10G22V Syrian rebels say storm Aleppo artillery base, army says attack repelled] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idUSKCN10G22V |date=20170115164608 }}, 2016-08-05.</ref><ref>[https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-devastates-largest-militant-offensive-ramousah-base-date/ Syrian Army devastates largest militant offensive on Ramousah Base to date] {{Wayback|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-devastates-largest-militant-offensive-ramousah-base-date/ |date=20201201212000 }}, 2016-08-05.</ref>攻入炮兵學校<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/ap/article-3725552/Danish-fighter-jets-drop-bombs-time-Syria.html |title=Syria rebels claim taking part of military college in Aleppo |access-date=2016-08-06 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427124625/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/ap/article-3725552/Danish-fighter-jets-drop-bombs-time-Syria.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。反對派隨後攻佔軍事學院更多地方，包圍圈內的反對派部隊也從東面進攻拉穆薩區，在兩面夾擊下，反對派成功佔領拉穆薩區並解除敘軍對阿勒頗東部的包圍，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3726662/Syria-rebels-key-positions-south-Aleppo-monitor.html |title=Syria rebels break Aleppo regime siege: opposition |accessdate=2016-08-06 |archive-date=2016-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806155224/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3726662/Syria-rebels-key-positions-south-Aleppo-monitor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是反對派在阿勒頗西南部新打通的通道仍受敘軍火力威脅而不安全。<ref name=dm20160806/>

「敘利亞人權觀察」表示從7月31日反對派發動解圍戰以來，至8月6日雙方合計有超過700名士兵陣亡，大部分是反對派，因為敘軍有空中優勢和得到俄軍密集空襲支援。單是8月6日一日內雙方合計已有200名士兵陣亡。7月31日至8月6日期間有至少130名平民在阿勒頗喪生，大部分是在反對派炮轟敘政府控制區時喪生。<ref name="500fighters">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3726838/At-500-fighters-killed-week-Aleppo-battle-monitor.html |title=At least 500 fighters killed in a week in Aleppo battle: monitor |accessdate=2016-08-06 |archive-date=2016-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217062652/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3726838/At-500-fighters-killed-week-Aleppo-battle-monitor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=dm20160806>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3727060/Syria-rebels-say-Aleppo-siege-broken.html |title=Syria rebels say Aleppo siege broken |access-date=2016-08-06 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427124635/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3727060/Syria-rebels-say-Aleppo-siege-broken.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 拉鋸戰 ==
8月11日，敘軍在拉穆薩區一帶發起自從反對派解圍以來的第一次反攻，初時有少許進展，但很快被反對派擊退。<ref>[http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-Rebels-Repel-HUGE-SAA-Attack-in-Aleppo/cjds/57ac563a0cf2460a62ee65b2 BREAKING: Rebels Repel HUGE SAA Attack in Aleppo!] {{Wayback|url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/ |date=20160830231409 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-foil-first-syrian-army-offensive-southern-aleppo/ |title=Jihadists foil first Syrian Army offensive in southern Aleppo |accessdate=2016-08-13 |archive-date=2016-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820203044/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-foil-first-syrian-army-offensive-southern-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月14日，老虎部隊在水泥廠的一次伏擊中據報造成了數十名[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]（前稱「努斯拉陣線」）和[[突厥斯坦伊斯兰党|突厥斯坦伊斯兰党]]武裝分子陣亡。在阿勒頗西部，反對派於Zahraa區發起的一次進攻被政府軍擊退。<ref name="Saif">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/battle-aleppo-field-report/|title=Battle of Aleppo: Field Report|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=14 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=15 August 2016|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202112954/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/battle-aleppo-field-report/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在隨後的夜間，敘軍與真主黨向1070房屋區發起反攻，政府方面宣稱在該區取得顯著進展。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-begin-counter-attack-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah begin counter-attack in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=15 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=16 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723020928/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-begin-counter-attack-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>經過8月15日一整日的戰鬥後，親政府部隊在俄軍空襲支援下終於在8月16日早上攻破反對派第一層防線，並控制1070小區約80%的地方。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-seize-80-percent-key-southern-aleppo-district/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah seize 80 percent of key southern Aleppo district|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=15 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=17 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723045648/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-seize-80-percent-key-southern-aleppo-district/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月17日，政府軍向早前失守的空軍技術學校發起反攻。領導該次反攻的Deeb Bazi-{准}-將是該校的司令官，在當日戰事中陣亡。<ref name="technical">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-syrian-army-storms-technical-base-southern-aleppo/|title=Field Report: Syrian Army storms Technical Base in southern Aleppo|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=17 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=18 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818171721/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/field-report-syrian-army-storms-technical-base-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>反對派的反攻最終逼使政府軍撤退。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-repel-syrian-army-attack-ramousah-base/|title=Jihadist repel Syrian Army attack on Ramousah Base|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=18 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=18 August 2016|archive-date=2019-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212170358/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-repel-syrian-army-attack-ramousah-base/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月18日，政府軍一度攻佔阿勒頗南郊的Al-Qarassi、Tal Sanourabat和-{Al-‘Amariyah}-三個村莊。反對派於同日稍後奪回該三個村莊。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-launch-new-assault-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah launch new assault in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=18 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=18 August 2016|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204154337/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-launch-new-assault-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jaysh-al-fateh-recaptures-lost-points-southern-aleppo/|title=Jaysh Al-Fateh recaptures lost points in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=18 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=18 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723013903/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jaysh-al-fateh-recaptures-lost-points-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月19日，[[叙利亚共和国卫队|共和國衛隊]]援軍從大馬士革抵達阿勒頗。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-reinforcements-pour-southern-aleppo-next-offensive/|title=Syrian Army reinforcements pour into southern Aleppo for next offensive|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=19 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=19 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723013852/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-reinforcements-pour-southern-aleppo-next-offensive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日敘軍向炮兵學校發起新的進攻，同時敘軍也向Al-Qarassi發起另一次進攻。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-launch-new-attack-key-military-site-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah launch new attack at key military site in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=19 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=19 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723010854/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-launch-new-attack-key-military-site-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在隨後的夜間，政府軍攻佔Tal Al-Aqra。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-launches-biggest-attack-key-military-base-southern-aleppo/|title=[Breaking] Syrian Army launches biggest attack on key military base in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=20 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=20 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723035618/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/breaking-syrian-army-launches-biggest-attack-key-military-base-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

至2016年8月中，雖然反對派部隊在本次戰役中死傷慘重，不過據報陣亡的大多是新兵，[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]等部隊的骨幹力量損失不大。<ref name=xh20160819>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-08/19/c_129241308.htm |title=阿勒颇之战何以胶着 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-08-19 |access-date=2016-08-27 |archive-date=2016-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002170921/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-08/19/c_129241308.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月21日，政府軍攻佔Umm Qara小山，從那裡可以俯瞰[[汗土曼|汗土曼]]（Khan Touman）－拉穆薩公路，<ref>[http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=49606 Continued clashes and advances for the regime in Aleppo] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220213955/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=49606 |date=2016-12-20 }}</ref>政府軍也攻佔了SyriaTel小山。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-syriatel-hill-southern-aleppo/ |title=Syrian Army captures SyriaTel Hill in southern Aleppo |accessdate=2016-08-24 |archive-date=2019-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514234132/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-syriatel-hill-southern-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!SAA-Counter-Attacks-in-South-Aleppo/cjds/57b9a3420cf2416a2e1cf879 SAA Counter Attacks in South Aleppo!] {{Wayback|url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/ |date=20160830231409 }}</ref>同日稍後，反對派的反攻逼使政府軍撤離Umm Qara。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-thwarts-jihadist-counter-offensive-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army thwarts jihadist counter-offensive in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=21 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=21 August 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107094314/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-thwarts-jihadist-counter-offensive-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月22日，親政府部隊控制了拉穆薩迴旋處和橋樑後，進攻炮兵學校，與防守該地的反對派爆發激戰。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-enters-key-military-base-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army enters key military base in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=22 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=22 August 2016|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723005341/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-enters-key-military-base-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，老虎部隊等敘軍試圖重奪Umm Qara山的控制權，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/battle-strategic-southern-aleppo-hilltop-intensifies/|title=Battle for strategic southern Aleppo hilltop intensifies|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=22 August 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=22 August 2016|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127233848/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/battle-strategic-southern-aleppo-hilltop-intensifies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>到8月23日終於成功。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-important-hilltop-southern-aleppo/ |title=Syrian Army captures important hilltop in southern Aleppo |access-date=2016-08-24 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107094332/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-important-hilltop-southern-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月30日，敘軍和真主黨部隊攻佔Tal Sanourbat小山。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-capture-tal-sanourbat-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah capture Tal Sanourbat in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2016-08-30|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723044135/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-capture-tal-sanourbat-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 敘軍第二次合圍 ==
9月2日，敘軍和真主黨部隊進攻軍械學校，<ref name="Armament School">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-attack-strategic-military-site-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army, Hezbollah attack strategic military site in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2016-09-02|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=2016-09-02|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915103249/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-hezbollah-attack-strategic-military-site-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>遇到防守的[[征服軍|征服軍]]頑強抵抗，攻守雙方都傷亡不少。到9月4日，以老虎部隊為首的敘軍聯同聖城旅攻佔軍械學校，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-military-base-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army captures strategic military base in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2016-09-04|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=2016-09-04|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917185553/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-military-base-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>敘軍與真主黨部隊再攻佔炮兵學校，其他敘軍則進攻空軍技術學校，<ref name="Artillery Base">{{cite web|url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-Artillery-Base-in-South-Aleppo-under-SAA-Control/cjds/57c9479dda6989244660cdd2|title=BREAKING - Artillery Base in South Aleppo under SAA Control!|publisher=The Inside Source|date=2016-09-04|accessdate=2016-09-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830231409/http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-Artillery-Base-in-South-Aleppo-under-SAA-Control/cjds/57c9479dda6989244660cdd2|archivedate=2016年8月30日|df=}}</ref>政府軍一方最終收復整個軍事學院建築群，再次包圍阿勒頗東部<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://in.reuters.com/article/mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idINKCN11A0QJ |title=Syrian government forces recapture areas in southwest Aleppo - monitor |accessdate=2016-09-05 |archive-date=2016-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916010540/http://in.reuters.com/article/mideast-crisis-syria-aleppo-idINKCN11A0QJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

9月5日，敘軍在阿勒頗南部攻佔更多地方。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-makes-huge-gains-southern-aleppo/|title=Syrian Army makes huge gains in southern Aleppo|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=5 September 2016|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=5 September 2016|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915145555/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-makes-huge-gains-southern-aleppo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-Rebel-Frontline-Collapses-in-South-Aleppo/cjds/57cd258c4c5873b76b3ef262|title=BREAKING! Rebel Frontline Collapses in South Aleppo!|date=5 September 2016|publisher=The Inside Source|accessdate=5 September 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830231409/http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-Rebel-Frontline-Collapses-in-South-Aleppo/cjds/57cd258c4c5873b76b3ef262|archivedate=2016年8月30日|df=}}</ref>9月8日，經過3天激戰後，政府軍完全收復拉穆薩區。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-district-southern-aleppo/ |title=Syrian Army captures strategic district in southern Aleppo |date=2016-09-08 |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107094402/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-district-southern-aleppo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在美國與俄羅斯新達成的敘利亞內戰停火協議於9月12日[[宰牲節|宰牲節]]日落時生效前，敘利亞政府表示同意停火，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/09-11/8000637.shtml |title=美俄斡旋达成叙利亚停火协议 支持和怀疑参半 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-09-11 |accessdate=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107094430/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/09-11/8000637.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>本次阿勒頗攻勢結束。停火屆滿後，敘政府軍在俄空軍支援下於9月22日發起[[阿勒頗攻勢_(2016年9月－12月)|新一輪攻勢]]。

